<p>When she was managing fashion brands for more than 20 years, she was following NGO’s and wanted to support one. Then she met İbrahim Betil during the establishment of the association, decided to join SEN DE GEL, and becomes a member of board of auditors. “I saw that we can touch the lives of people living in far away places, even with very small amounts. Join SEN DE GEL for a better world.”</p>